name: Two Discounted Tickets - EZ BREEZY SPECIAL
description:
Two LOWER LEVEL tickets to the Breeze home opener at St Pete Times Forum on 10/21 
YOUR Tampa Breeze will be hosting the newest LFL expansion team, Cleveland Crush.

With the purchase of these tickets, your name will be entered TWICE into a drawing to win an autographed photo of Tampa Breeze star veteran #5 Eliese "EZ BREEZY" Zukelman

First drawing takes place on 8/26 during halftime of the LFL's season kickoff game.
